name: Free To Play Sci Fi Fantasy MMO! (Canceled)
blurb: This Free To Play MMORPG Is a Sci-Fi Influenced Universe with Fantasy Elements. In a setting where Nature and Tech will collide.

rewards.reward: Everything counts in large amounts!  Your dollar gets you a special thanks on our Facebook page and once it is launched you will be listed on a Special Thanks area on our Website!!!
Precious!!! Your hard earned money gets you a pack of Shiny Images showing off the various Races to obsess over. All Rewards above are included.
Nothing says Alpha like a Beta! You get the play the game before the Unwashed Masses.  Access to all early demo's, plus all the Goodies above it.

Special Award:\r\nNow you can have as much Fashion Sense as we do.  Sport your rockin' CritterBox Stewdio T-Shirt and be the Envy of all.  This Reward is only available for this particular pledge.  Limited Numbers available.  Plus you can also wear it while enjoying all the Goodness above this!
Steal This Game! Get a FREE Copy of our completed game (with a generous donation of $75 or more, of course!).  You don't need to steal the swag above because we will give you that too!

Who said Trolls cannot be born with a Silver Spoon?  Get a leg up on the competition with the Survival pack.  This provides you with Better starting Armor & Weapons, a nice wad of Credits, and some Healing items.  A great way to begin the game, with all the goodies listed above to accompany you.
Tour the world with a friend in your new Ride.  Get another copy of the game and a Limited Edition Vehicle with a low number of Models in existence. With extra trunk space for all the items above it.

Everyone will Fear and Respect you, just like Godzilla!  Not only will you be listed in the Game Credits, with your name wrapped in Shiny Gold Goodness!   Both the Game World will learn to Fear your presence with your Exclusive Uber Powerful Weapons & Armor.  Did we forget to mention you get the thingies above it?

Break out the Cardboard and Boombox, It's time for some old school moves.  If no one likes it, then sick your new friend on them.  Here you get an extra set of moves, known to a select few, and a Pet from a near extinct race of creatures.  Also, your very special to us and will be listed as a Producer in the credits.  Plus the stuff in the text above this.   Who knows you may even be accidentally sent a T-Shirt?

Hey! Wait a minute, is that?  Yeah, It's you.  What are you doing here, you ask? Well it's because your extra special and we contacted you to be simulated into our world.  So now your one of those NPC things.  Don't you remember?  Well, here's all the stuff up there to help you remember.   Maybe even a T-Shirt might jog your memory.

We're not selling out, we're buying in!  At this level you can feature your product in our game, be it a beverage, clothing name, or waffles.  Now if you don't have a product (or want another choice), then you can write an Award winning Quest for our game!  You can use all the prizes above this for Inspiration.
